1
00:03:04,180 --> 00:03:10,060
[The Perfect Suspect]

2
00:03:11,010 --> 00:03:13,610
[Episode 15]

3
00:03:35,710 --> 00:03:37,190
Your daughter came back hurt,

4
00:03:37,190 --> 00:03:38,790
and you're just ignoring it?

5
00:03:42,310 --> 00:03:43,640
I want to care about her,

6
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,680
but as soon as I get close to her,

7
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,840
she gets scared.

8
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:51,030
It's my own fault.

9
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,450
The psychologist said,

10
00:04:03,180 --> 00:04:05,280
she's easily triggered right now.

11
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:08,000
Maybe we should give her some time.

12
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,730
After her emotions stabilize,

13
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,000
we'll come again.

14
00:04:12,910 --> 00:04:13,440
Let's go.

15
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,680
Yang Yan and I were good friends.

16
00:04:37,430 --> 00:04:40,430
Who gave you that book
Rainbow of the Little Princess?

17
00:04:40,830 --> 00:04:42,070
Yang Yan gave it to me.

18
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:44,020
When did she give it to you?

19
00:04:45,430 --> 00:04:46,510
A long time ago.

20
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:50,750
Why did Yang Yan give you this book?

21
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,040
Because...

22
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:59,430
she told me she had a secret hideout

23
00:04:59,659 --> 00:05:01,230
in this book.

24
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:04,500
I really missed her,

25
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:07,310
so I followed this book

26
00:05:08,310 --> 00:05:10,640
to find the secret hideout she mentioned.

27
00:05:13,510 --> 00:05:14,390
And then...

28
00:06:05,410 --> 00:06:06,940
Help! Help!

29
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,830
I want to go home.

30
00:06:24,330 --> 00:06:25,860
Don't you like it here?

31
00:06:26,890 --> 00:06:28,340
This is your home now.

32
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,390
See if this suits you.

33
00:06:45,310 --> 00:06:48,270
I'll be your mom from now on, okay?

34
00:06:54,870 --> 00:06:55,680
Zixuan,

35
00:06:57,920 --> 00:07:01,120
we hope you'll be honest with us.

36
00:07:03,430 --> 00:07:04,480
To be honest,

37
00:07:06,310 --> 00:07:08,870
although Ms. Wang Ya kidnapped me,

38
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,920
she was really kind to me.

39
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:17,630
Even more kind than my mom.

40
00:07:27,070 --> 00:07:30,310
One more question.
I've asked you before,

41
00:07:31,010 --> 00:07:32,470
but I need to ask again.

42
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:36,170
It's okay. Think carefully
before you answer, okay?

43
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,270
When did Yang Yan give you

44
00:07:40,550 --> 00:07:42,810
the book Rainbow of the Little Princess?

45
00:07:48,970 --> 00:07:50,020
Hide and seek.

46
00:07:50,930 --> 00:07:51,520
[Tianfu Supermarket
National Chain Store]

47
00:07:51,520 --> 00:07:54,270
We thought the killer was hiding—

48
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:57,480
but now it seems that in this game,

49
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,680
what's really hidden

50
00:07:59,090 --> 00:07:59,930
is the child.

51
00:08:00,990 --> 00:08:02,510
We've analyzed before

52
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,270
what kind of motive

53
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,600
could make Liao Boyan willing to

54
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:09,330
work with the person
who killed his daughter.

55
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,840
If it's for the sake of the child,

56
00:08:12,310 --> 00:08:14,270
that's all the motive he'd need.

57
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,720
You're a father too.

58
00:08:19,150 --> 00:08:20,200
What do you think?

59
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:24,630
Liao Boyan is also a father.

60
00:08:25,630 --> 00:08:27,190
He must have known

61
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:30,310
that Liao Yifan's heart was
transplanted to Yang Yan.

62
00:08:30,310 --> 00:08:31,920
That's why he got involved in a series of

63
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,510
events related to Yang Yan.

64
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:39,789
That's the motive and reason.

65
00:08:41,030 --> 00:08:41,669
Keran,

66
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:44,390
do you have any
photo materials of Yang Yan?

67
00:08:44,390 --> 00:08:45,010
Yes.

68
00:08:45,270 --> 00:08:48,270
Find that elementary school
graduation group photo.

69
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:51,510
Here.

70
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:55,590
I've seen this photo before.

71
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,630
It struck me as odd at the time,

72
00:08:57,630 --> 00:08:59,630
but I didn't think much of it. Look.

73
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,240
Yang Youmo was here.

74
00:09:02,780 --> 00:09:04,130
Luo Lijuan was here.

75
00:09:05,570 --> 00:09:07,370
Then who was Yang Yan looking at?

76
00:09:08,510 --> 00:09:09,030
[Graduation Ceremony of Class 2015]

77
00:09:09,030 --> 00:09:11,510
Could you please show us all the photos

78
00:09:11,510 --> 00:09:12,570
taken at that time?

79
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:14,370
Okay, let me look for them.

80
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:17,120
I keep all the graduation photos

81
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,650
of the children every year.

82
00:09:19,030 --> 00:09:20,160
Take a look at these.

83
00:09:21,050 --> 00:09:22,430
[Graduation Ceremony of Class 2015]

84
00:09:24,870 --> 00:09:25,720
Wait.

85
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,260
Could you zoom in a bit?

86
00:09:29,330 --> 00:09:30,140
Here?

87
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,240
Yes, right there.

88
00:09:39,510 --> 00:09:42,110
These two have known
each other for a long time.

89
00:09:43,740 --> 00:09:47,200
[Nanying District Sub-Bureau
Xinggang City Public Security Bureau]

90
00:09:49,340 --> 00:09:50,140
Take a look.

91
00:09:55,610 --> 00:09:57,000
[Graduation Ceremony of Class 2015]

92
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:11,590
Liao Boyan.

93
00:10:14,790 --> 00:10:16,510
You told us a story.

94
00:10:18,990 --> 00:10:20,430
Now let me tell you one—

95
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:25,630
a story about a father.

96
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,480
There was a father

97
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:33,100
who loved his daughter very much.

98
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:36,000
But then a car accident

99
00:10:38,520 --> 00:10:40,320
took his daughter away forever.

100
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:47,440
The weather feels comfortable
back in the country, right?

101
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:48,600
Yeah.

102
00:10:50,190 --> 00:10:52,350
Dad, I'll treat you to ice cream.

103
00:10:54,390 --> 00:10:56,790
You just want some
for yourself, don't you?

104
00:10:56,910 --> 00:10:58,120
I'll buy one for each of us.

105
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:59,080
Three flavors.

106
00:11:01,970 --> 00:11:03,050
Slow down.

107
00:11:03,950 --> 00:11:05,640
The ice cream will melt.

108
00:11:08,270 --> 00:11:09,730
Our daughter has grown up.

109
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:11,350
She's still a kid.

110
00:11:11,750 --> 00:11:13,160
Well, you said that.

111
00:11:13,790 --> 00:11:14,510
She's still a kid.

112
00:11:14,510 --> 00:11:16,910
Why do you always
take her around like this?

113
00:11:17,900 --> 00:11:20,440
I wonder if she can adapt to settling down

114
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,720
back in the country.

115
00:11:22,100 --> 00:11:24,560
As long as there's ice cream,
she'll be fine.

116
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,510
Thank you.

117
00:11:41,790 --> 00:11:45,020
Since then, his life's
been plunged into darkness.

118
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:49,700
There's no light

119
00:11:50,550 --> 00:11:51,810
left in his life at all.

120
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:04,380
A friend at the hospital said,

121
00:12:05,950 --> 00:12:08,180
if we both sign to donate,

122
00:12:11,140 --> 00:12:12,320
Yifan's heart

123
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:14,440
could save another child's life.

124
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:24,550
You...

125
00:12:25,570 --> 00:12:26,120
You...

126
00:12:39,990 --> 00:12:42,580
[Voluntary Registration Form
for Organ Donation in China]

127
00:12:42,580 --> 00:12:44,260
[Name: Liao Yifan
Occupation: Student]

128
00:12:44,260 --> 00:12:45,950
[Relationship: Liao Boyan (Father)
Relationship: Tan Qing (Mother)]

129
00:12:45,980 --> 00:12:53,570
[Signature of Donation Registrants:
Liao Boyan, Tan Qing]

130
00:13:07,040 --> 00:13:09,830
You and Tan Qing
donated Liao Yifan's heart.

131
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:13,470
Organ donation should
follow the double-blind principle,

132
00:13:13,470 --> 00:13:16,680
but you failed to overcome your obsession,

133
00:13:17,610 --> 00:13:19,240
and illegally found out

134
00:13:19,520 --> 00:13:21,890
the information of the heart recipient.

135
00:13:26,460 --> 00:13:28,120
[Organ Transplant Record 2010–2012]

136
00:13:28,140 --> 00:13:30,290
[Cardiology, Urology, Hepatology]

137
00:13:30,410 --> 00:13:34,540
[Cardiology, Heart Transplant,
Liao Yifan, Yang Yan]

138
00:13:50,750 --> 00:13:52,920
You started paying attention to Yang Yan

139
00:13:52,920 --> 00:13:54,750
and tried to get close to her.

140
00:13:55,890 --> 00:13:58,220
You treated Yang Yan as your own daughter.

141
00:13:58,480 --> 00:14:01,490
You wished even more that
she could be your daughter.

142
00:14:03,870 --> 00:14:10,610
♪ Snow turns to ice, then melts to water ♪

143
00:14:10,990 --> 00:14:17,150
♪ Water rises as vapor,
then falls as rain ♪

144
00:14:18,150 --> 00:14:24,710
♪ Raindrops into the sea,
from the sea swims a fish ♪

145
00:14:25,370 --> 00:14:31,350
♪ Swimming upstream for thousands
of miles, just to return home ♪

146
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:38,750
♪ Waiting for you, across the vast land ♪

147
00:14:39,510 --> 00:14:46,020
♪ Running to you,
with tears but no words ♪

148
00:14:46,650 --> 00:14:47,690
♪ Holding you, never part again ♪

149
00:14:47,690 --> 00:14:49,850
So you made a bold decision—

150
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:53,560
[Rainbow of the Little Princess]

151
00:14:53,560 --> 00:14:54,540
to stay by her side,
protect her in your own way,

152
00:14:54,540 --> 00:14:58,370
♪ Loving you, so my soul can rest ♪

153
00:14:58,370 --> 00:14:59,900
and make her your princess.

154
00:15:14,910 --> 00:15:15,840
Goodbye, sir.

155
00:15:29,360 --> 00:15:35,870
♪ Snow turns to ice, then melts to water ♪

156
00:15:36,580 --> 00:15:42,740
♪ Water rises as vapor,
then falls as rain ♪

157
00:15:43,730 --> 00:15:50,330
♪ Raindrops into the sea,
from the sea swims a fish ♪

158
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:56,790
♪ Swimming upstream for thousands
of miles, just to return home ♪

159
00:15:57,770 --> 00:15:59,050
♪ Waiting for you, across the vast land ♪

160
00:15:59,050 --> 00:16:02,880
Your protection also made her
more dependent on you.

161
00:16:03,280 --> 00:16:04,280
Gradually,

162
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:05,040
her dependence on you is even
greater than that on her family.

163
00:16:05,040 --> 00:16:11,610
♪ Running to you,
with tears but no words ♪

164
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:16,110
♪ Holding you, never part again ♪

165
00:16:16,110 --> 00:16:18,050
You knew Yang Yan's life

166
00:16:18,680 --> 00:16:20,020
and her family situation.

167
00:16:20,020 --> 00:16:21,270
♪ Loving you, so my soul can rest ♪

168
00:16:21,270 --> 00:16:23,200
Come on, three...

169
00:16:29,250 --> 00:16:29,900
[Going to see my baby brother later.
I'll send a pic.]

170
00:16:31,750 --> 00:16:33,750
But what you didn't expect was that

171
00:16:34,390 --> 00:16:36,190
there's an evil beside Yang Yan.

172
00:16:38,440 --> 00:16:40,790
In order to be with Zhao Qian,

173
00:16:41,510 --> 00:16:43,910
Yang Youmo actually
harmed his own family.

174
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,320
Under the repeated mental abuse

175
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:54,030
from Yang Youmo and Zhao Qian,

176
00:16:54,710 --> 00:16:56,930
Yang Yan's mother jumped from a building.

177
00:16:56,930 --> 00:16:58,720
It looked like suicide.

178
00:17:07,750 --> 00:17:10,880
Yang Yan's little brother
also fell victim to fate.

179
00:17:12,609 --> 00:17:13,630
At first,

180
00:17:13,940 --> 00:17:15,700
you didn't realize

181
00:17:15,720 --> 00:17:17,450
how much danger Yang Yan was in.

182
00:17:28,540 --> 00:17:31,580
In the end, Yang Yan also
died tragically.

183
00:17:32,210 --> 00:17:34,620
And you were filled with regret.

184
00:17:57,230 --> 00:17:58,680
You're right.

185
00:18:03,270 --> 00:18:05,880
I didn't realize she was in danger.

186
00:18:10,930 --> 00:18:13,080
If I had realized earlier,

187
00:18:16,540 --> 00:18:17,880
she wouldn't have...

188
00:18:30,920 --> 00:18:31,580
Zhong Ning,

189
00:18:32,470 --> 00:18:33,440
I remember now.

190
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:34,880
Remember what?

191
00:18:34,960 --> 00:18:38,270
I remember how Zhao Qian and Yang Youmo

192
00:18:39,330 --> 00:18:41,850
tried twice to kill Yang Yan.

193
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:45,610
Twice.

194
00:19:12,110 --> 00:19:12,860
Dad,

195
00:19:12,880 --> 00:19:14,440
the seatbelt is stuck.

196
00:19:24,850 --> 00:19:27,200
Dad, slow down. I'm scared.

197
00:20:00,260 --> 00:20:01,400
Are you okay?

198
00:20:25,600 --> 00:20:26,650
Thank you, Dad.

199
00:20:32,720 --> 00:20:34,920
Actually, I was a bit scared yesterday.

200
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:36,160
The seatbelt got stuck,

201
00:20:36,160 --> 00:20:37,780
and the car was going so fast.

202
00:20:38,030 --> 00:20:39,480
Dad was scared too.

203
00:20:41,050 --> 00:20:43,150
Luckily, nothing happened.

204
00:20:45,160 --> 00:20:46,270
Remember this,

205
00:20:46,790 --> 00:20:49,320
always buckle up first
when you get in the car.

206
00:20:55,030 --> 00:20:56,270
Come on, eat.

207
00:20:58,200 --> 00:20:59,460
Thank you, Uncle Liao.

208
00:21:07,510 --> 00:21:08,400
Liao Boyan,

209
00:21:09,880 --> 00:21:11,940
you were hiding behind Fang Qinchun.

210
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:14,160
and Zhang Qiaoyun.

211
00:21:16,070 --> 00:21:19,400
And Wang Ya was hiding behind you.

212
00:21:22,090 --> 00:21:24,150
She used to be an excellent engineer.

213
00:21:25,240 --> 00:21:26,830
Without her help,

214
00:21:27,680 --> 00:21:30,200
you couldn't have installed monitoring app

215
00:21:30,270 --> 00:21:31,590
on Yang Youmo's phone,

216
00:21:32,150 --> 00:21:35,750
or modified the altimeter for murder.

217
00:21:39,840 --> 00:21:42,040
This painting's Zhao Lin's final work.

218
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:44,800
Look at the brushwork—

219
00:21:44,960 --> 00:21:46,290
definitely authentic.

220
00:21:46,590 --> 00:21:48,450
Please check it carefully for me.

221
00:22:17,510 --> 00:22:19,520
Why isn't there any reaction at all?

222
00:22:24,050 --> 00:22:26,240
Something must've gone
wrong in the operation steps.

223
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:28,040
We need to get close to him again.

224
00:22:32,190 --> 00:22:33,650
It shouldn't be like this.

225
00:23:10,700 --> 00:23:12,560
I've never seen you smoke before.

226
00:23:13,350 --> 00:23:15,000
It's from my ex-wife.

227
00:23:40,290 --> 00:23:42,670
I saw her being swept away by the water.

228
00:23:42,690 --> 00:23:46,010
Without a body, we can't be certain.

229
00:23:46,060 --> 00:23:47,830
I'm just saying, what if,

230
00:23:48,800 --> 00:23:52,090
what if one day she comes back alive?

231
00:23:52,120 --> 00:23:53,840
You know what I would do.

232
00:23:54,310 --> 00:23:55,200
Youmo,

233
00:23:55,800 --> 00:23:58,350
I really don't want to see you like this.

234
00:23:58,890 --> 00:24:00,670
It makes me feel guilty.

235
00:24:01,030 --> 00:24:02,830
But I don't regret it—

236
00:24:03,790 --> 00:24:04,850
because I love you.

237
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:09,510
Zhao Qian and Yang Youmo must die.

238
00:24:11,070 --> 00:24:14,240
Otherwise, Yang Yan won't survive.

239
00:24:32,250 --> 00:24:34,980
I asked if you'd ever
been to that amusement park.

240
00:24:35,940 --> 00:24:38,000
You said you had, with your daughter.

241
00:24:38,970 --> 00:24:41,500
At the time, I thought
you were just confused.

242
00:24:42,440 --> 00:24:45,000
Because your daughter
passed away five years ago.

243
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:48,440
And that park has been
open for less than two years.

244
00:24:50,070 --> 00:24:51,270
Now I understand.

245
00:24:52,750 --> 00:24:56,030
The daughter you mentioned was Yang Yan.

246
00:25:15,460 --> 00:25:18,560
♪ Beautiful sunflower ♪

247
00:25:19,840 --> 00:25:22,810
♪ Growing branches in the dark night ♪

248
00:25:23,890 --> 00:25:27,960
♪ Gazing at the vast distance ♪

249
00:25:28,260 --> 00:25:31,300
♪ Quietly waiting ♪

250
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:37,870
♪ Blood-red sunflower ♪

251
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:42,080
♪ Standing strong against wind and rain ♪

252
00:25:43,250 --> 00:25:46,510
♪ Guarding a distant place in the heart ♪

253
00:25:46,510 --> 00:25:47,650
Xie Xiaohua and Yang Yan
were fellow patients.

254
00:25:47,650 --> 00:25:50,870
♪ Stubbornly growing ♪

255
00:25:50,870 --> 00:25:52,780
After Yang Yan transplanted Liao Yifan's heart,

256
00:25:52,780 --> 00:25:54,830
♪ Glorious bloom on a long, long road ♪

257
00:25:54,830 --> 00:25:56,950
she still had contact with Xie Xiaohua.

258
00:25:56,950 --> 00:25:57,920
So,

259
00:25:57,950 --> 00:25:58,280
you knew about
Xie Xiaohua's family situation.

260
00:25:58,280 --> 00:26:01,130
♪ But you're no longer here ♪

261
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:01,430
You also knew that his father, Xie Wuqiang,

262
00:26:01,430 --> 00:26:03,640
♪ The sunflowers look up at the sky ♪

263
00:26:03,640 --> 00:26:05,120
was dealing illegal meds.

264
00:26:06,120 --> 00:26:06,920
Right?

265
00:26:06,950 --> 00:26:09,720
♪ Wondering where home is ♪

266
00:26:10,160 --> 00:26:14,880
♪ The long road, swaying and drifting ♪

267
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:18,960
♪ Whose gaze is fading away? ♪

268
00:26:19,680 --> 00:26:21,880
♪ Who hums the song of fate? ♪

269
00:26:21,880 --> 00:26:23,230
That's the real reason

270
00:26:24,020 --> 00:26:24,350
♪ The sunflowers still bloom ♪

271
00:26:24,350 --> 00:26:26,580
you killed Yang Youmo and Zhao Qian.

272
00:26:26,580 --> 00:26:29,400
[Medical Record
of Nan Ying Hospital, Xinggang City]

