comprehensive medical examination.

303
00:28:03,400 --> 00:28:06,730
It was confirmed that
he doesn't have Alzheimer's disease.

304
00:28:14,480 --> 00:28:16,270
But I still trust my instincts.

305
00:28:18,310 --> 00:28:19,960
He used memory loss to shift our focus,

306
00:28:19,960 --> 00:28:22,770
rule out his suspicion, or maybe—

307
00:28:24,160 --> 00:28:25,960
behind the amnesia and silence,

308
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:28,440
he's still hiding some secrets.

309
00:28:31,790 --> 00:28:33,270
What secret could it be?

310
00:28:35,360 --> 00:28:38,390
[Nanying District Sub-Bureau
Xinggang City Public Security Bureau]

311
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:45,420
Director Zhang.

312
00:28:45,420 --> 00:28:46,550
-Director Zhang.
-Director Zhang.

313
00:28:46,550 --> 00:28:47,400
